Class BasePresenter<V extends MvpView>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codepath.musichunter.ui.base.BasePresenter<V>

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DisplayLyricsByTrackMvpPresenterIml, DisplayTracksByAlbumMvpPresenterIml, SearchAlbumByArtistPresenterImpl, SearchByArtistPresenterIml, SearchTopTenLovedTracksByArtistMvpPresenterIml

    public class BasePresenter<V extends MvpView>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MvpPresenter<V>
    Base class that implements the Presenter interface and provides a base implementation for onAttach() and onDetach(). It also handles keeping a reference to the mvpView that can be accessed from the children classes by calling getMvpView().
